prove yourself to us.

96
00:05:44,208 --> 00:05:46,541
What? No that's not
what I'm doing at all!

97
00:05:46,625 --> 00:05:49,583
Oh. Does that mean you still
want to be our advisor?

98
00:05:49,666 --> 00:05:50,750
