00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,166
And you need
to swear to God.

105
00:06:03,250 --> 00:06:04,708
I swear!

106
00:06:04,791 --> 00:06:07,375
Also, if you ever tell me again
that you're going to quit.

107
00:06:07,458 --> 00:06:09,958
You won't mind if I strip
you naked, take pictures,

108
00:06:10,041 --> 00:06:11,458
and spread them all
over the internet?

109
00:06:11,541 --> 00:06:12,791
No, I won't!

110
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:15,416
Really? How nice.

111
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:17,291
Let's have a round of
applause for our new advisor,

112
00:06:17,375 --> 00:06:19,541
Maria Takayama.

113
00:06:19,625 --> 00:06:21,458
