embarrassing me.

116
00:06:26,625 --> 00:06:29,250
Don't worry; I'll take
care of everything, stupids!

117
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:33,083
We're gonna need you to
clean the room every other day.

118
00:06:33,166 --> 00:06:34,541
But at the moment
I'm thirsty,

119
00:06:34,625 --> 00:06:35,916
so some tea
would be great.

120
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,208
I'll get it!

121
00:06:39,333 --> 00:06:41,000
There's nothing easier
than fooling a fool

122
00:06:41,083 --> 00:06:42,000
am I right guys?

123
00:06:44,125 --> 00:06:45,791
Somebody is watching you?

124
