127
00:06:57,416 --> 00:06:59,458
I mean think about
it for a second!

128
00:06:59,541 --> 00:07:01,208
Ninety percent of stalkers
stalk because they think

129
00:07:01,291 --> 00:07:02,791
they're in love
with their victim.

130
00:07:02,875 --> 00:07:04,375
Have you had anything
remotely resembling

131
00:07:04,458 --> 00:07:06,000
a romance since coming
to this school?

132
00:07:07,375 --> 00:07:08,916
Shut up! First,
that's not true,

133
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,083
and B, I shouldn't have asked.

134
00:07:11,166 --> 00:07:13,666
Hold on just a second.

135
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:16,833
I'm not about to let a fellow
club member suffer alone.

136
00:07:16,916 --> 00:07:19,000
Today's club focus.
Helping you.

137
00:07:19,083 --> 00:07:20,625
Let's catch your stalker.

138
00:07:23,291 --> 00:07:26,375
Yep. I'm definitely getting
the feeling we're being watched.

139
00:07:26,458 --> 00:07:29,500
True. This was not just
your imagination, Kodaka.

140
00:07:29,583 --> 00:07:33,291
