not what I was talking about.

141
00:07:33,375 --> 00:07:34,750
I don't know why, but
every single person

142
00:07:34,833 --> 00:07:37,125
we pass is giving me the
freaking evil eye!

143
00:07:37,208 --> 00:07:38,541
How am I supposed
to find a stalker

144
00:07:38,625 --> 00:07:39,958
with this crap going on?

145
00:07:40,041 --> 00:07:41,833
