very own set of rules

202
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:02,416
and does whatever he wants to do
whenever he wants to do it!

203
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,916
He's brave yet feared!

204
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,458
He takes what he
wants from whomever,

205
00:10:05,541 --> 00:10:06,916
but is never greedy.

206
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,583
And he gets rid of people
who refuse to do what he says.

207
00:10:09,666 --> 00:10:11,541
All while surrounded
by gorgeous ladies

208
00:10:11,625 --> 00:10:12,916
who do his bidding.

209
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,875
He neither knows nor
shows fear of God,

210
00:10:14,958 --> 00:10:17,500
because he is the lord of
his own heaven and earth!

211
00:10:17,583 --> 00:10:18,875
That dude is from
a different anime!

212
00:10:18,958 --> 00:10:20,875
I always follow
school rules,

213
00:10:20,958 --> 00:10:22,250
and have never
stolen anything.

214
00:10:22,333 --> 00:10:24,041
And women do not serve me!

215
00:10:24,125 --> 00:10:25,583
Add modesty to that list.

216
00:10:25,666 --> 00:10:27,041
Someone help!

217
00:10:27,125 --> 00:10:28,416
Let's break this down.

218
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:30,416
The bottom line is you are
trying to become someone

219
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:32,125
who would never
get bullied.

220
00:10:32,208 --> 00:10:34,041
How do people bully
you in the first place?

221
00:10:34,125 --> 00:10:35,958
The boys in my class
leave me out of

222
00:10:36,041 --> 00:10:37,625
whatever they're
doing all the time.

223
00:10:37,708 --> 00:10:40,458
Like, for example,
when we've got gym.

224
00:10:40,541 --> 00:10:42,041
Every time I start
to change my clothes,

225
00:10:42,125 --> 00:10:44,416
they run off as
fast as they can.

226
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:46,083
It's so mean.

227
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:48,833
And when we play
like, dodgeball.

228
00:10:48,916 --> 00:10:50,708
They never even
try to hit me.

229
00:10:50,791 --> 00:10:53,458
Um. How's that bad?

230
00:10:53,541 --> 00:10:55,333
Poor, poor Yukimura.

231
00:10:55,416 --> 00:10:57,375
That's the saddest
thing I've ever heard.

232
00:10:57,458 --> 00:10:59,000
I'm pretty sure they
treat me this way

233
00:10:59,083 --> 00:11:00,958
because they're all
convinced I'm a girl.

234
00:11:01,041 --> 00:11:02,291
But I just know
it will stop

235
00:11:02,375 --> 00:11:04,583
if I become manlier
like you, Kodaka!

236
00:11:05,791 --> 00:11:07,958
You are an inspiration.

237
00:11:08,041 --> 00:11:09,291
Not a lot of people
are willing to face

238
00:11:09,375 --> 00:11:11,541
their difficulties
head on like you do.

239
00:11:11,625 --> 00:11:13,083
It's brave.

240
00:11:13,166 --> 00:11:14,625
I think you should
thoroughly study the art

241
00:11:14,708 --> 00:11:16,833
of becoming a man with
our resident thug.

242
00:11:16,916 --> 00:11:18,541
That's so sweet of you.

243
00:11:18,625 --> 00:11:20,208
However.

244
00:11:20,291 --> 00:11:23,375
Kodaka is very busy with our
Neighbor's Club activities.

245
00:11:23,458 --> 00:11:25,125
If you were to join
the group as well,

246
00:11:25,208 --> 00:11:26,333
then you'd get the chance

247
00:11:26,416 --> 00:11:28,416
to observe him in
his natural habitat.

248
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:29,875
I'm so in.

249
00:11:29,958 --> 00:11:31,666
Why didn't you treat me
like that when I joined?

250
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,166
Okay, what's your angle?

251
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:34,333
Fess up.

252
00:11:34,416 --> 00:11:35,875
What's the big problem?

253
00:11:35,958 --> 00:11:37,583
You're getting your
own personal underling.

254
00:11:37,666 --> 00:11:39,875
This way, you'll be
the consummate delinquent.

255
00:11:39,958 --> 00:11:41,291
Why would I want that?

256
00:11:41,375 --> 00:11:43,250
Do you really mean it?

257
00:11:43,333 --> 00:11:46,041
